# Project Description

## Overview

This is a Google Chrome extension that helps users understand the real cost of items by converting prices into hours of work required.

## Features

### 1. Hourly Wage Storage

- The extension stores the user's hourly wage locally
- Wage data persists across browser sessions

### 2. Hourly Wage Management

- Users can view their current hourly wage
- Users can update/change their hourly wage at any time

### 3. Price-to-Hours Conversion

- When the extension is activated on a website, it automatically:
  - Detects if the current website is a shopping/e-commerce site
  - Identifies item prices on the page
  - Converts each item's price to the number of hours the user would need to work to afford it
  - Displays the conversion alongside or near the original price

## Use Case

This extension helps users make more informed purchasing decisions by providing a tangible perspective on the cost of items in terms of their time and labor.

